{"tid":819932,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"慈父帶新抱揀樓 預5球入市","createTime":"2018-09-15T07:00:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-15T09:50:10.000Z","uid":10101,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7ec5da72b49aeab66a5e877db4a00cd6bb76366b","tid":819932,"uid":10101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T07:00:44.000Z","msg":"南豐旗下將軍澳日出康城LP6今日賣488伙，準買家鄺生同新抱一齊到場，幫阿仔兩夫婦揀樓，他們一家都住在將軍澳區，於區內有私人物業，是次抽得70多號籌，打算購入LP62房單位，預算500多萬元入市換樓，認為價錢比同區屋苑來說不算貴。<br />\n<br />\n鄺生指，阿仔已婚是文員，是次入市的首期如阿仔要幫手，他都會一起分擔。至於樓市走勢，他認為是自住唔驚升定跌，每個人有自己睇法。近期有部份發展商推十成按揭，惟需要以已經供滿的私人樓作為抵押，鄺生則表示是次入市不需要將單位抵押。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180915/58684866\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180915%2F58684866&d=%2FJ%2FZ3zBmxpWOjrIK420EkjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=24028ad5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180915%2F58684866&h=fc229bbf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180915/58684866</a><br />\n<br />\n認真講，咁重要，邊有理由唔係一個人出席？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/150037_a8fd2b732a04403045362edcbcec0ca9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F150037_a8fd2b732a04403045362edcbcec0ca9.png&h=9ca914cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b25019dfd05e5bc801a157ed8e84b54bb74f73b","tid":819932,"uid":10101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T07:01:04.000Z","msg":"一家人"},{"pid":"6c25ac4e22061ed27ac40f8bc475f5f118229f0a","tid":819932,"uid":66590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T07:12:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓爆啊 冇人買架啦 蝕死你地"},{"pid":"4a31e7afa373614255c9f2dc3cce6304425b0685","tid":819932,"uid":40397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T07:44:17.000Z","msg":"要幫個孫（定仔呢？）準備下<br />\n唔係爺載就父幹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff8a52f061d7e049f4ef4703b1d13ec782127655","tid":819932,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a31e7afa373614255c9f2dc3cce6304425b0685","tid":819932,"uid":40397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T07:44:17.000Z","msg":"要幫個孫（定仔呢？）準備下<br />\n唔係爺載就父幹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T07:47:01.000Z","msg":"新抱 變 後母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16ce43ccb9ed10055ab96c8a65de3325e984ac2b","tid":819932,"uid":17434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T08:08:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd342ca4236da5e79698b033c454eca3837cb7a1","tid":819932,"uid":3167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T08:11:52.000Z","msg":"望到張圖一半以為睇緊個盤嘅模型<br />\n屌"},{"pid":"953fdf575df9feb2013267917c30c7cb3e3b40bf","tid":819932,"uid":153239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd342ca4236da5e79698b033c454eca3837cb7a1","tid":819932,"uid":3167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T08:11:52.000Z","msg":"望到張圖一半以為睇緊個盤嘅模型<br />\n屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T08:13:27.000Z","msg":"岩呀<br />\n睇盤骨呀嗎<br />\n睇住個盤 好生養<br />\n屌得過<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5728c440b294c06a8e2a28275c3a33bb8172578","tid":819932,"uid":20928,"like":0,"dislike":0